<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to SetHealth</title>
    <style>
      /* General styling */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333333;
        background-color: #f4f4f9;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #eee;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #007bff;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .content p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #dad8d8;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to SetHealth!</h1>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Section -->
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello Dr. <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>We’re excited to welcome you to SetHealth! Our platform is dedicated to helping doctors like you connect with patients, manage consultations effortlessly, and grow your practice.</p>
        <p>To get started, please complete your registration by clicking the button below:</p>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" class="button">Complete Registration</a>
        </p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our support team at any time. We're here to help you make the most of SetHealth.</p>
        <p>Welcome aboard, and here’s to a successful journey together!</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer Section -->
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 SetHealth. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="[Your Privacy Policy Link]" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="[Your Terms Link]" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none;">Terms of Service</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
